				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The air pet does generate a lot of aggro via stuns, but for most tanks these days it's not enough to turn a mob onto pet if the tank goes out of range.  It has happened to me before in groups, but never on a raid.  
<br />

<br />
If it's really a problem for your guild's MT to keep aggro over WoX then: taunt off and/or water pet should take care of it.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=431972" target="_blank" class="postlink">Stren Tiendar</a>
