				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>chaosmage wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">But as it has beet stated before, pets cannot get aggro over players.  All the aggro from the pet goes to the closest pc.  So how is your pet even getting aggro over the ma?</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
