				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">For <span style="font-style: italic">positioning </span>you should consider that WoX will often stun the mob if not marked "unstunnable." Most, if not all "bosses" are so marked, but trash generally is not. Sending in WoX before the mob is positioned can cause the mob to "freeze" for a couple seconds and not follow the MT/puller. It has nothing to do with aggro.
<br />

<br />
EDIT -- Bottom line? Wait for /assist<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=568700" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Itchyban of Veeshan</a></span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by itchyban on Fri Jan 30, 2004 10:13 pm; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
