then again my guild tends to actually use pets to move the mob to a corner.  playing tank-pong with a summoning mob is just begging for him to go oor of clerics and die.  our standard strat is mass zerg pet swarm while the tank guides the mob backward to the corner.  learn to USE pets instead of complaining that pets stop you from doing something you probably shouldn't be doing anyway.  you can corner anything anywhere in 20 seconds with a competent tank and he'll never be summoned so he can keep building aggro.
